msgstr "[Dépannage](#6-troubleshooting)"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:13
msgid "1. Overview"
msgstr "1. Aperçu"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:15
msgid ""
"ZeroClaw routes MQTT/webhook/cron/peripheral events through a unified SOP "
"dispatcher (`dispatch_sop_event`)."
msgstr ""
"ZeroClaw achemine les événements MQTT/webhook/cron/périphériques via un "
"répartiteur SOP unifié (`dispatch_sop_event`)."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:17
msgid "Key behaviors:"
msgstr "Comportements clés :"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:19
msgid ""
"**Consistent trigger matching:** one matcher path for all event sources."
msgstr ""
"**Correspondance cohérente des déclencheurs :** un seul chemin de "
"correspondance pour toutes les sources d'événements."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:20
msgid "**Run-start audit:** started runs are persisted via `SopAuditLogger`."
msgstr ""
"**Audit de début d'exécution :** les exécutions démarrées sont persistées "
"via `SopAuditLogger`."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:21
msgid ""
"**Headless safety:** in non-agent-loop contexts, `ExecuteStep` actions are "
"logged as pending (not silently executed)."
msgstr ""
"**Sécurité sans tête :** dans les contextes hors boucle d’agent, les actions "
"`ExecuteStep` sont consignées comme en attente (et non exécutées "
"silencieusement)."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:23
msgid "2. MQTT Integration"
msgstr "2. Intégration MQTT"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:25
msgid "2.1 Configuration"
msgstr "2.1 Configuration"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:27
msgid ""
"Configure broker access with `zeroclaw config set channels.mqtt.<field> "
"<value>` — the keys land under `[channels.mqtt]` in the stored config. See "
"the [Config reference](../reference/config.md) for all fields. The `use_tls` "
"flag must match the scheme of `broker_url` (`mqtts://` ⇒ `true`, `mqtt://` ⇒ "
"`false`)."
msgstr ""
"Configurez l’accès au courtier avec `zeroclaw config set channels.mqtt."
"<field> <value>` — les clés sont placées sous `[channels.mqtt]` dans la "
"configuration stockée. Consultez la [Référence de configuration](../"
"reference/config.md) pour l’ensemble des champs. Le drapeau `use_tls` doit "
"correspondre au schéma de `broker_url` (`mqtts://` ⇒ `true`, `mqtt://` ⇒ "
"`false`)."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:29
msgid "2.2 Trigger Definition"
msgstr "2.2 Définition du déclencheur"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:31
msgid "In `SOP.toml`:"
msgstr "Dans `SOP.toml` :"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:33
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"sensors/alert\"\n"
"condition = \"$.severity >= 2\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"sensors/alert\"\n"
"condition = \"$.severity >= 2\"\n"
"```"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:40
msgid ""
"MQTT payload is forwarded into SOP event payload (`event.payload`), then "
"shown in step context."
msgstr ""
"Le payload MQTT est transféré dans le payload de l'événement SOP (`event."
"payload`), puis affiché dans le contexte de l'étape."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:42
msgid "3. Webhook Integration"
msgstr "3. Intégration de Webhook"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:44
msgid "3.1 Endpoints"
msgstr "3.1 Points de terminaison"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:46
msgid ""
"**`POST /sop/{*rest}`**: SOP-only endpoint. Returns `404` if no SOP matches. "
"No LLM fallback."
msgstr ""
"**`POST /sop/{*rest}`** : Point de terminaison uniquement pour les SOP. "
"Retourne `404` si aucune SOP ne correspond. Pas de fallback LLM."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:47
msgid ""
"**`POST /webhook`**: chat endpoint. It attempts SOP dispatch first; if no "
"match, falls back to normal LLM flow."
msgstr ""
"**`POST /webhook`** : point de terminaison de chat. Il tente d'abord la "
"dispatch SOP ; en cas d'absence de correspondance, il revient au flux LLM "
"normal."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:49
msgid "Path matching is exact against configured webhook trigger path."
msgstr ""
"La correspondance des chemins est exacte par rapport au chemin de "
"déclenchement du webhook configuré."

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:53
msgid "Trigger path in SOP: `path = \"/sop/deploy\"`"
msgstr "Chemin de déclenchement dans SOP : `path = \"/sop/deploy\"`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:54
msgid "Matching request: `POST /sop/deploy`"
msgstr "Requête de correspondance : `POST /sop/deploy`"

