#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:796
msgid "A change to `channel-discord` does not recompile the kernel"
msgstr ""
"Une modification apportée à `channel-discord` ne recompilera pas le noyau."

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:797
msgid "Contributors working on a plugin only recompile their plugin"
msgstr ""
"Les contributeurs travaillant sur un plugin ne recompilent que leur plugin."

#: src/foundations/fnd-001-intentional-architecture.md:798
