msgstr "« ERREUR : référence introuvable »"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:32
msgid "2. Collect and categorise commits"
msgstr "2. Collecter et catégoriser les commits"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:34
msgid "Collect"
msgstr "Collecter"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:37
msgid "\"%H %h %s\""
msgstr "\"%H %h %s\""

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:40
msgid "Save full SHAs for the contributor resolution step:"
msgstr ""
"Enregistrer les SHAs complets pour l'étape de résolution des contributeurs :"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:43
msgid "\"%H\""
msgstr "\"%H\""

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:46
msgid "Categorise"
msgstr "Catégoriser"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:48
msgid ""
"Map each commit to a section by its conventional commit prefix. Commits "
"without a recognized prefix must still be read and categorized by content — "
"never silently drop them."
msgstr ""
"Associez chaque commit à une section en fonction de son préfixe de commit "
"conventionnel. Les commits sans préfixe reconnu doivent toujours être lus et "
"catégorisés par leur contenu — ne les ignorez jamais silencieusement."

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:52
msgid "`feat:`, `feat(*)`"
msgstr "`feat:`, `feat(*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:52
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:65
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:144
msgid "What's New"
msgstr "Quoi de neuf"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:53
msgid "`fix:`, `fix(*)`"
msgstr "`fix:`, `fix(*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:53
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:66
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:165
msgid "Bug Fixes"
msgstr "Corrections de bugs"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:54
msgid "`refactor:`, `perf:`"
msgstr "`refactor:`, `perf:`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:54
msgid "What's New (group as \"Improvements\")"
msgstr "Quoi de neuf (groupe comme « Améliorations »)"

